cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with anomaly detection through video analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses object recognition and optical flow, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with surveillance videos, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR).
